            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>S</abbr><ex>ilvano</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>omestico</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>acrum</ex></expan> et <lb n="2"/>Magl<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>Sep</abbr><ex>timi--</ex></expan> Val<supplied reason="lost"><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/></supplied><lb break="no" n="4"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> e<supplied reason="lost">t</supplied> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr><supplied reason="lost">Se</supplied>p</abbr><ex>timia</ex></expan><certainty match="preceding-sibling::node()" locus="value"/> Val<supplied reason="lost"><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/></supplied><lb break="no" n="6"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> filia <lb n="0"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Nach Scherrer sehr wahrscheinlich eine moderne &amp;lt;span style=&amp;apos;color:red&amp;apos;&amp;gt;Fälschung&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt;. Z. 3 u. 5: vom L jeweils nur die senkrechte Haste erhalten. Z. 4: vom P nur die obere Hälfte erhalten. Reste von roter Farbe in den Buchstaben. (B): Böhm - Weber: Z. 2: Magl(ae); Taeuber; Böhm - Weber; Scherrer: Z. 4: [---]P [et].</p>
            </div>
